Territory2ModelHistory.name: Territory2ModelHistory
Territory2ModelHistory.description: Represents the history of changes to the values in the fields on a territory model.

DataType.description: Data type of the field that was changed.

Field.description: The name of the field whose value was changed.

NewValue.description: The new value of the changed field.

OldValue.description: The previous value of the changed field.

Territory2ModelId.description: The ID of the territory model whose history is tracked.
